  "remarks": "Member of the Rajah Solaiman Movement (QDe.128) and linked to the Abu\nSayyaf Group (QDe.001). Father's name is Fernando Rafael Dellosa. Mother's name is\nEditha Parado Cain. In detention in the Philippines as of Jan. 2010. Review pursuant to\nSecurity Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 13 May 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.  INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
